        <h4>Horario de atención</h4>
        <div class="footer-contact-block">
          <p><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg> Lun - Vie: 3:00 p.m. a 10:00 p.m.</p>
          <p><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg> Sábados: 2:00 p.m. a 7:00 p.m.</p>
        </div>
